Program board:
>> sudo cp firmware/nrf52832_xxaa.hex /media/$USER/JLINK




ONLY IF YOU MODIFY THE FIRMWARE CODE --> to compile:

Install gcc (version 7-2017-q4-major):
>> bash install_gcc.sh


Compile the firmware: 
>> cd src
>> make GNU_INSTALL_ROOT=$HOME/gcc-arm-none-eabi-7-2017-q4-major/bin/ -C pca10040


Program board:
>> sudo cp pca10040/_build/nrf52832_xxaa.hex /media/$USER/JLINK
